"Mindlink"        
        This allows the psionicist to use his telepathic powers to send
        messages to others.  Effectively a psion style tell.  A nice guild
        perk (once it has been bought) in keeping with the psionicist theme.
 
SP Cost:  2		Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  mindlink, ml, mlrep, mlrepto
